title: English Vinglish
subTitle: A housewife and caterer, Shashi, is usually mocked by her family for not knowing English. Her attempt to learn the language helps her rediscover herself and reassert her value as a mother and a wife.

title: Tigers : Can a Salesman be a Hero
subTitle: Ayan, a pharmaceutical salesman, decides to stand against his company after discovering that their new baby formula is responsible for the death of many babies..

title: Sniff
subTitle: Sunny, who lacks the sense of smell, finds his olfactory abilities enhanced after becoming a victim of a laboratory accident, which turns him into a superhero.

title: Saheb, Biwi Aur Gangster 3
subTitle: Madhvi Devi relishes her political power but worries about losing it upon her husband Aditya's release from prison. To prevent this, she recruits Uday, a gangster, to assassinate him.

subTitle: Armed with state-of-the-art equipment and a brilliant plan, National Security Guard commandos risk their lives to save innocent people caught in a terrorist attack on a temple in Gujarat.

title: Karthik Calling Karthik
subTitle: Karthik leads a taxing life as a scorned office worker until his own voice offers him the key to love and prosperity over a series of early morning phone calls.

title: Zero
subTitle: A vertically-challenged bachelor with a larger-than-life personality discovers his life's purpose through his relationships with two wildly different women.

title: Salaam Venky
subTitle: Sujata, an ideal mother, faces the biggest challenge of her life when her son is diagnosed with muscular dystrophy. Despite this, she is determined to help her child live life to the fullest.

title: Naam Shabana
subTitle: Shabhana, desperate for justice, agrees to join a secret intelligence agency in exchange for their help in unmasking her friend's murderer.

title: Goodbye
subTitle: A family crumbles when the mother suddenly passes away and the children try to rush home to complete her final rites. However, differing opinions cause clashes among the clan.

title: Mission Majnu
subTitle: An undercover Indian spy takes on a deadly mission to expose a covert nuclear weapons program in the heart of Pakistan that could destroy the free world.

title: Sherdil: The Pilibhit Saga

title: Joggers' Park
subTitle: Jyotin Chatterjee, a former judge, falls for Jenny, a young and independent woman. However, things take a turn when his family scrutinises their relationship.

title: Akaash Vani

title: Attack

title: Sam Bahadur

title: Judgementall Hai Kya
subTitle: Bobby, a dubbing artist who is haunted by a childhood trauma, rents out a portion of her house to Keshav and Rima. However, she repeatedly stalks the young couple and is suspicious of Keshav.
